snippet.title: ETERNAL CODE | A Secret Technology Puts the World at Risk | Full Movie
snippet.description:
A breakthrough technology sparks a dangerous power struggle.
Saving her family means uncovering the truth behind it.

When a powerful CEO refuses to approve an illegal life-sustaining device, she and her husband are taken by force. With time running out, their daughter is pulled into a hidden world where science, greed, and ambition collide. To save her parents, she must form an unlikely alliance and expose a secret that powerful people will do anything to protect.

Director: Harley Wallen
Cast: Scout Taylor-Compton, Richard Tyson, Billy Wirth, Mel Novak, Calhoun Koenig.
